| Operator | Description         | Syntax |
| -------- | ------------------- | ------ |
| &        | Bitwise AND         | x & y  |
| \|       | Bitwise OR          | x \| y |
| ~        | Bitwise NOT         | ~x     |
| ^        | Bitwise XOR         | x ^ y  |
| \>>      | Bitwise right shift | x>>    |
| <<       | Bitwise left shift  | x<<    |

